CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 3, 1952, pg. 30, reads: " Cage Champions - One of the last teams in district to be crowned was the Sewickley Community basketball team, shown above, winners of the United Neighborhood Houses of Allegheny County cage title.  Members of the team are, left to right, first row: Barnette, Greene, Tucker and Boykin.  Second row: Lee, Shackleford, Williams, E. R. Lewis, executive director and coach; Jackson, Jones, Gilmore and Redwing. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Sewickley Community Center basketball team, front row from left: Barnette, Greene, Tucker, and Boykin; second row: Lee, Shackleford, Williams, coach E. R. Lewis, Jackson, Jones, Gilmore, and Redwing, posed in gymnasium
